channel.title: Help me get my server online please
channel.description:
Hey I can't get port forwarding to work. I use a Netgear DG834PN router and whenever I put the IP address I use for No-IP in to the "Send to LAN Server" space, it says "IP Address is illegal!".
Any help PLEASE.
